                  and our team will review it soon.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div
                className="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-1"
                style={{ backgroundColor: "var(--bg-secondary)" }}
              >
                <div className="h-full bg-green-500 animate-[progress-shrink_2.5s_linear_forwards]" />
